-- MOVES-Andreas Costa joins CR Investment as associate director
-- 
-- Wed Jul 23, 2014 05:39AM EDT
-- None



July 23 (Reuters) - CR Investment Management, a European financial advisory firm, said it appointed Andreas Costa associate director.

Based in the company's London office, Costa will be responsible for expanding the debt and equity origination functions and the underwriting and distribution of performing and non-performing loans, CR said.